summary: This mod adds the "Wilson! Oh no!" death sound from Gorgeous Freeman.
descriptionHtml: Upon dying be welcomed by the oh-so-beautiful[url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nPr-Nl1khHU] "WILSON! OH NO!"[/url] sound effect. There's not much to say, except that I got inspired/stole the way to do it from [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/2210879]xchargerfanx's[/url] [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/5794]"Super Mario Death Sound"[/url]﻿. Full credit to him and [url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrjImfv2PReA1VhEfNaDOYw]Antoine Delak[/url]﻿.
author: KrycerKris
